Description: Contains functions to create new data sets compatible with
    the 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d' packages for plotting brain segmentations
    through R. Requires several external software to be installed on the
    system for atlas creations to work, and most of these are not
    available for windows.  But atlas creation tools exist for 2d simple
    features data, and also 3d tri-surface mesh plots. Also has a list of
    compatible data sets and functions for easy installation of these.
